Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.40,0:01:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山是分了七層\N由神僊居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.50,0:01:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了打倒支配這座山的\N邪惡帝皇多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.07,0:01:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向第七界層進發的我們\N終於到了第七界層的魔神殿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.04,0:01:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然在那裏展開了\N和多惡達的最後之戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.21,0:01:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但對全部武器\N也起不了作用的多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.82,0:01:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們變得束手無策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.48,0:01:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上多惡達\N喚醒了暗黑龍來對付我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.55,0:02:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰王丸、幻王丸和空王丸\N也受了傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.69,0:02:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在想已不行的時候\N失去了東哥羅的虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.43,0:02:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用邪虎丸撞向了暗黑龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.66,0:02:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在多惡達用憤怒之力\N打倒了邪虎丸的瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.33,0:02:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和龍王丸的聲音一起\N從變成了石像的龍王丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.97,0:02:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,體內飛出了一條金龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.84,0:02:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也會是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.84,0:02:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十四話\N閃耀吧!創界山的彩虹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.55,0:02:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老虎,老虎,振作點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.62,0:02:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,張開眼睛啊,老虎,老虎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.79,0:02:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老虎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.70,0:02:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟反抗父親真是蠢材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.50,0:02:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要乖乖聽話便是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.07,0:02:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太過分了,絕對不能饒恕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.24,0:02:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼欺負老虎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.81,0:03:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡\N你怎樣也要打倒多惡達啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.95,0:03:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了打倒多惡達\N我可以把這條命交給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.59,0:03:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.19,0:03:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.26,0:03:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世伯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.03,0:03:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.96,0:03:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經沒有什麼可以再教你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後只要全心全意作戰便是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.50,0:03:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.97,0:03:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,加油!\N你要替老虎報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多惡達,決勝負吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.58,0:03:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不自量力,讓我盡情給你\N品嚐一下魔界的恐怖吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便進攻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.27,0:03:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,暗黑龍應該\N還留下邪虎丸給它的傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.14,0:03:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,你捉緊了,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.64,0:04:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那處了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.62,0:04:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,就這樣撞上去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.22,0:04:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是機會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.63,0:04:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.14,0:04:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎可以輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不打倒多惡達的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.11,0:04:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山便不能恢復和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.55,0:04:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!\N渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.02,0:04:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.12,0:05:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.69,0:05:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.39,0:05:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是龍神之盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.83,0:05:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.01,0:05:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.72,0:05:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是機會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.86,0:06:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多惡達,受死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍被…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.27,0:06:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的劍可以打倒多惡達嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.96,0:06:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…龍王之劍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,這個第七界層的地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.87,0:06:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有唯一能打倒多惡達的武器\N龍王之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.91,0:06:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能拔出龍王之劍\N便能變成真正的救世主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.31,0:06:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔出那把劍\N便能戰勝多惡達了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.11,0:06:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,現在剩下的手段\N只有那把劍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我拔不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.09,0:07:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.86,0:07:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要迷惘了,渡\N這樣下去會被暗黑龍追上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.73,0:07:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機會只有一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.49,0:07:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.86,0:07:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要有自信\N你是創界山的救世主啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.96,0:07:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了,是龍王之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.64,0:08:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神…神部七龍神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.30,0:08:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你終於\N能把龍王之劍拔出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.02,0:08:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多惡達就是因為\N害怕龍王之劍的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.52,0:08:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而把它用魔力變成石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.92,0:08:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多惡達可以封印它\N卻沒有力量破壞它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.30,0:08:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.60,0:08:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用龍王之劍\N打倒多惡達的時刻到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.93,0:08:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把龍王之劍用雙手舉上天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.11,0:09:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偉大的天之時,神部七龍神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.38,0:09:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在真正的救世主名下\N合為一體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.81,0:09:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍王之劍竟然甦醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來了,多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.25,0:09:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.96,0:09:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.30,0:09:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山的真實支配者\N多惡達的真正恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.13,0:09:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給你看清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.25,0:10:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,舉起龍王之劍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.07,0:11:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多惡達,受死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.40,0:11:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成…成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.14,0:11:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.04,0:11:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬歲!萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.41,0:11:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了,世伯\N咦?世伯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.08,0:11:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.42,0:11:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔,你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.29,0:12:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的父親,幻龍齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.46,0:12:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的父親不是猴子嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.83,0:12:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真無聊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.04,0:12:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是猴子比較有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.61,0:13:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看,老婆婆\N創界山的彩虹全部恢復七色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.05,0:13:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡把多惡達打倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.83,0:13:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虎王,振作點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.27,0:13:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山恢復和平了,虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.61,0:13:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.48,0:13:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.71,0:13:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.58,0:13:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…和你是…好、朋、友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.46,0:13:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,我們是好朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.00,0:13:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虎王!虎王!…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.44,0:14:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老虎,不可以死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.08,0:14:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虎王!老虎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.90,0:14:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老虎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.00,0:14:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.27,0:15:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是聖龍妃女皇和翔龍子王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.64,0:15:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.38,0:15:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老虎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.90,0:15:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被多惡達封印在暗黑龍內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.93,0:15:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連兒子翔龍子也被變成虎王\N被多惡達控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.84,0:15:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,很多謝你拯救了創界山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.65,0:15:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.98,0:15:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本王子記不起一直以來的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.32,0:15:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到的是你把母后\N從暗黑龍中救了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.86,0:15:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還用身體保護了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.59,0:16:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,很多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.20,0:16:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你,虎王…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.63,0:16:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,翔龍子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.47,0:16:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老虎,你的說話方式很怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.87,0:16:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,不可以這麼失禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.28,0:16:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫火美子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.95,0:16:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像有點記得你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.39,0:16:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得你照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.00,0:16:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老虎說過要我做他的新娘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.76,0:16:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新娘?\N火美子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.70,0:16:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,打倒了多惡達的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.84,0:16:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有你們的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.01,0:16:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會成為救世主傳說\N流傳下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.33,0:17:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你終於完成了\N這麼艱苦的使命,做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.86,0:17:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為有很多朋友幫助\N我才能完成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.37,0:17:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?\N就這樣留在這麾沙村好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.47,0:17:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有等我回去的人呢\N我還是回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.58,0:17:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?會變得很寂寞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.05,0:17:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,火美子\N世伯,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.29,0:17:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然發生了很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.82,0:17:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但全靠大家\N我都能越過了,謝謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.92,0:17:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空氣話不用說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.09,0:17:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回到原來的世界\N也不要忘記我們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.56,0:17:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可能會忘記\N我會經常記著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.93,0:17:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你還會回來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.10,0:17:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還會再來的,一定!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.12,0:18:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.66,0:18:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你是在下的徒弟\N也不要忘記啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.09,0:18:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論什麼時候\N也要有不畏劍傷的勇氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.46,0:18:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.67,0:18:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,再下去分手時更痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.84,0:18:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,要分別了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.54,0:18:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸在龍神池等你,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.15,0:18:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位,保重了,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.95,0:18:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你要活得健康啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.19,0:18:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜拜,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.13,0:18:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,這麼長的戰鬥\N你也能忍耐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.80,0:18:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣你也是個出色的男人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.77,0:19:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的很努力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.38,0:19:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,我真的不想回去\N我想一直和龍神丸一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.22,0:19:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,我經常也在你身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要你望向天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.17,0:19:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在雲裏面,在彩虹裏面\N在星裏面也有我在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.87,0:19:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,抹掉眼淚吧,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.28,0:19:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,我不會再哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.52,0:19:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.06,0:19:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.38,0:20:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.65,0:20:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了,師傅、火美子\N世伯、古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.75,0:20:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了,創界山的各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.52,0:20:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還會…還會再見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.96,0:20:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.89,0:20:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,加油啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.69,0:20:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次再玩吧,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.74,0:21:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.84,0:21:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回到原來的世界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.75,0:21:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山…那些全部是夢嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.42,0:21:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我那天確是在學校\N做了個龍神丸的紙粘土…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.03,0:21:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是夢嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.50,0:21:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.84,0:21:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,是龍神丸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.44,0:21:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那果然不是夢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.18,0:21:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是做夢,不是做夢啊!

